[font=Comic Sans MS][b]Having trouble running good fps in Skyrim?
Is your computer just so old that you can't even boot Skyrim?
Well if you answered yes to any of those questions, this is the perfect mod for you.
This mod can simply give almost any computer, better fps in Skyrim.
All the mod does is reduce the size/resolution of in-game textures, making Skyrim less of a load on your computer.Â 
Also increases loading times.
Be sure too endorse the mod if it was useful! Thanks![/b][/font]
